data.description: This exquisite 4-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom custom all-brick ranch is a masterpiece of design and luxury living. Inviting Great rm w/gas fpl, EIK boasts top-of-the-line appliances, including a Sub-Zero refrigerator & Wolf stove, center island, custom shelving w/designer finishes & a large butler's pantry w/wine cooler seamlessly flow into the Formal Dining rm. Possible in-law suite w/BR & FBTH. Lavish MBR Suite, complete w/its own fpl, his & her wlk-in closets and spa-like MBTH offering a jacuzzi, steam shower & sauna. Enjoy the convenience & security of a Lutron lighting system, an 8-zone camera system, state-of-the-art Russound system. California closets, hwd flrs and Pella windows add to the luxury. Full fin bsmt w/an outside entrance from the drvwy, offers a large Kitchen, custom built-in wet bar, granite counter tops, theater rm, wine cellar, large gym w/rubber flooring & full Bth. 17 zone radiant heat, utility rm w/custom shelving & a full wlk-up attic. Park w/ease, spacious 3 car gar, circular drvwy, that offers plenty of rm for pking! Step outside to the covered patio and spacious blue stone masonry deck, overlooking the park-like property. It's the perfect backdrop for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Enjoy the convenience of living close to major highways, NJ/NYC transportation, shopping, schools, dining, entertainment & more! Don't miss this extraordinary opportunity to make this custom ranch your forever home!.
